Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:06.51,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Welcome everyone to Wednesday Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:11.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's move on with the first presenter if you would please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:21.07,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hakata Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Teacher. Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:26.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Weren't the fan girl screams for Teach impressive?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okazoe-san, if I may ask suddenly, have you ever found money
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you had forgotten about in your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite often actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Often? \NWhat, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:40.61,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You forget about it often?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.57,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,With money it's like second-nature to just stash it away when you find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:45.37,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:54.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I feel like she's not very good at holding this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that money is yours you can do that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:00:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, this time I present you all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:09.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When you find money that you don't know about in your pocket, you will most definitely stash it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When you find it in your own clothes of course you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Isn't this my money?" and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something you'd normally do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:25.80,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Well, when it's like 1000 yen (~$10)...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.47,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It depends on how much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.47,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It does depend on how much...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You definitely wouldn't find a large amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of the amount, it does matter and that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,, This time, it's 50,000 yen (~$500).
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:33.97,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With $500 I'd definitely wonder if it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:39.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ebisu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's from my pocket then it's mine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about whether it's yours or not, just that you find $500.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would put money in my pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That person can only be me (so it's mine).
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:59.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Coming up, planting money into pockets secretly! An observation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I win it from the slots..?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:07.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After that, "Caricatures of scary customers will be greatly weakened for some features"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:13.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then, "The rewards on a point card system become far more ridiculous towards the end" as well as
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:17.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first Ghost-Bicyclist Championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes! He strikes a winning pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:43.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When you find money that you don't know about in your pocket, you will most definitely stash it away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:48.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first target is Viking's Kotoge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With cooperation from Television magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:57.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,a photo shoot featuring fashionable comedians will take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:04.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The magician playing as a cameraman will plant $500 in Kotoge's pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.36,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,How will this play\N out, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The accomplice Shoji waits for
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:13.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the unsuspecting Kotoge to enter the studio
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.79,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oooh! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.76,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:17.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Immediately, the photo shoot featuring fashionable private clothes begins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:20.83,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They're wearing their own private clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you do something like this please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand a little closer together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to have people standing close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:31.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While Kotoge poses, the magician begins to make his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly. Bring your chin up-- perfect. Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:41.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First, he uses his finger to make the pocket accessible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.08,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn a little this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.65,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then face the front, please. Angle your arms forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:51.99,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Whoa, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.72,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's fast. Really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.34,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's nimble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:57.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He makes a blind spot using crossed arms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:02.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,from which he easily plants all five $100 in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:05.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please put your hands in your pockets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have like a cellphone please take that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You put money in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717.857,959.286)}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You the type to go without a wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717.857,959.286)}No, not at all..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot to keep in a pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you perhaps forget you had that there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I would know about $500 though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(460.714,813.571)}I really don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(456.429,819.286)}This doesn't feel right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Upon finding money he doesn't remember having,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kotoge feels uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Manager) What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why but this is here..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:06.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To entice him, his manager brings him his wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't feel right at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:19.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to be pocketing the money
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here we reveal ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Wednesday Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717.857,959.286)}You've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you didn't put the money you found away. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were $100...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I would think that MAYBE I left that in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But finding $500?? That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of money is scary isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't feel right at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you want to put dirty money in your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We kind of felt you would though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know about it, Shoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU KNEW!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell do YOU know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:21.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next target is Sanshiro's Komiya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:26.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time, disguised as a group of three fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:31.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,one of them will place $500 in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698.571,645)}Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:39.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While waiting for his partner, some fans call out to him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Komiya's fan huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:45.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As they distract him, $500 is snuck into his clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.95,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:50.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Without suspecting a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:57.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Komiya moves to the next location
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please change your clothes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your valuables away in your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:03.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You would \Nbe surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:15.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Komiya finds the $500
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.93,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's putting it away \N- Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:25.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He double checks the amount of money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.88,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,There he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.20,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He kept it, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and stashes it away in his wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:39.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that, we now approach Komiya
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717.857,959.286)}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened? That you've come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In your pocket, there was $500 wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, my pocket--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.. Why do you know? How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you said..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it really isn't mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, not at all. We put it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, see, 'cause it was there I felt it was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, of course it wouldn't happen. $500!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? That's too large of an amount to find suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if it was like $10 or $20 maybe it'd make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even some coins. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.46,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's talking so\N freaking much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.80,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He totally is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot to say
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717.857,959.286)}Yeah... Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:24.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that said, the fact that Komiya stashes the money away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,does not necessarily make Komiya a bad person
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.88,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.28,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.94,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That is SO embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We leave that as a disclaimer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:35.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that, our final target is Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.57,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He will TOTALLY\N go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.79,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Will Kuro-chan \Ndo it I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:40.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like with Kotoge, we set up for a fake photo shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just like that. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you raise your arms a bit? Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:50.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Using the same tactic with he blind spot, $500 is slipped into the pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.96,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you check your pockets? They're bulging out a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure your wallet or cell phone aren't in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(285,416.428)}Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.39,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.79,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Don't involve him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this money here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that from the slots?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite an amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717.857,959.286)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get it from the slots?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,(End of the photo shoot)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would please, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it belong to the stylist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's mine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm gonna put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:40.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Into the wallet goes the $500
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,His image is\Nin danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:44.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, the money is stashed away
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:51.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Unlike Kotoge and Komiya, he was \Nadamant about the money being his
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.78,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:56.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Before the experiment can end, there is one more thing to be verified
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:08.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,TBS has called him out for a fake DVD interview
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:14.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,During the photo shoot, the staff will infiltrate Kuro-chan's dressing room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:23.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There they will put 100,000 yen (~$1000) in his bag, twice the former amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.21,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,How evil
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for buying :3
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa wa waaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, it's kind of weird without some confetti
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think adding the confetti would give us a solid ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be smooth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you go get some for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:45.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan is sent back to the dressing room to get him to look in his bag
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.72,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah, he noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:14.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He noticed the 100,000 yen, but just put it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:18.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and returned to the set
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thaaaaaank youuuu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa wa waaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:26.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that, the shooting ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and Kuro-chan returns once again to the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:34.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He takes out the money he placed earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He checks the amount
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:48.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Without fail, he stashes the money in his wallet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wooo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo OooO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:04.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He starts humming a cheerful tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:08.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Suspect: Kurokawa Akihito, AKA Kuro-chan, Age 39
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of course, we must investigate further (2 days later)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:19.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time, we are placing hidden camera's inside the target's home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:25.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...And placing 1 million yen (~$10,000) in his doorstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:30.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will Kuro-chan pocket this money as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:33.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That shit is wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2 hours later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:41.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan returns without knowing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The result is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.88,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh you put it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:06.99,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He must be scared thinking someone's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, what the hell? What the hell??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:22.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,More than the 1 million yen, Kuro-chan is more afraid that someone was in his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.20,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:35.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For some reason, he eccentrically rings his own doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.91,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What is he doing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is here right? Someone is here right??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Right??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's pretty scary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.02,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't come out!(even if someone was there)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.86,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What's up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is here right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx103\fscy127}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx130\fscy157}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx153\fscy202}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx178\fscy226}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx211\fscy265}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I being loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You gonna close it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, someone is here right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do anything, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!? Hello!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.04,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,"I wont do anything, I promise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No one!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Super scary, what the hell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?? What??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:42.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:44.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that, it's time for the reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.43,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So scary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:56.01,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's scary but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.13,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah, he covered it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Wednesday Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what do you mean? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up hold up hold up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get this at all, hold up, what? what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anything strange happened to you lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange things...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I was in a meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...there was nothing but extremely sexy people there. Are you talking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:53.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He doesn't notice what happened, so this time we have to explain it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that you're hiding there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind lifting up that bag for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No... you're mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.01,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,No he's not
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that I would pocket this money. Seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn I was super scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was freaking terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:22.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There you have it, having 1 million yen placed in your house while you're away is super scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Downtown, what would you guys do in that situation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,if you opened up a drawer and took out 1 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If I found it in my drawer then I would take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hmm, a drawer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at their level, they would just say "Oh, just 1 million?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:47.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,First of all, the price of me versus Hamada is way different
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:50.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,About 8:2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,8:2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done really well for yourself then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty successful
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:04.70,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Moving on, our next presenter, please come forward
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:15.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Sanshirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You came as a combination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is my new consort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best as the main and sub of Sanshirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You have a dirty body don'tcha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,From the previous scene right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.09,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure you're both filthy actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:34.73,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Of course you too, no matter how you look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty livid right now aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I get yelled at that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've thought "What a pitiful body" from looking at my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Pretty shameful yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, this is sudden, but everyone please take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is from a manga called Gorillaman, "Ghostriding"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned about it from the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,While riding a bike, you first let go of the handlebars...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,... and due to the momentum as you get off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...it appears as if a ghost is riding the bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.99,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Just with bicycles though
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So with that, our theory is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:18.89,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Theory: A Ghostriding Tournament will be reasonably exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gathered some people who seem like they would be good at ghostriding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to their image
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And we were thinking "Won't this be interesting"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we wanted to try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:39.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Theory: A Ghostriding Tournament will be reasonably exciting" investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:46.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We've gathered 4 challengers to take part in this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:48.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our first contender...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:55.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,BMX Pro Rider: Ikeda Takahiro
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.74,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh, he seems really good
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:59.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,2016 BMX National Runner Up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:04.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Currently holding 4 Guinness World Records, he's a bike expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:10.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's also performed in the Cirque du Soleil
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like there are a lot of people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,who used to do this when they were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I also did it when I was a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It ends up curving left or right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be important to try and make the bike go straight
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our next contender...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:31.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Former Women's Keirin Athlete, Shimano Reibin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:37.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She just retired from the sport 2 months ago, after winning the Girl's Championship 8 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:39.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Holding the weight of those accomplishments,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:43.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,she suddenly decided to take part in this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:47.60,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow, her ass is sticking out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's not it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:50.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Competing on behalf of the entertainment world, Yasuda's Big Circus's Danchou
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:55.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's competed in numerous road races and triathlons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:20:00.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's also passed the corporate team's entry test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically all they use is Kuro-chan right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He always gets super excited
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the end he is always just being deceived
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurokawa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You take a good look
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Lastly
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:26.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gymnastics Athlete Ozeki Shingo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,His power is in maintaining balance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:31.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When thinking about ghostriding ,the most critical point would be balance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Placing his faith in his balance, he joins the competition
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In all, these four are the ones competing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:42.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ghostriding Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.08,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Eh, that seems fun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:45.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The rules are simple: As soon as you throw the bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:50.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The bicycle which goes the furthest shall be declared the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The recorded distance is not based on the path taken
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but the straight line distance from the starting point
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:59.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for us, the day begins with rain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We decided to hold the bicycle championship indoor instead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:08.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The contestants have three choices
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:13.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mama-chari Bike*, Mountain Bike and Road Bike
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:13.31,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\pos(199,202)}* A family bike
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.05,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Woah, amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:09.05,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:16.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By drawing lots, the first contestant is chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yasuda Dai Circus : Danchou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:20.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So his choice is the mama-chari bike
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:24.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We witness his first ghost bike try
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:25.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:28.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,140,000 yen is the cost of his beloved bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:32.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is good enough to be employed by a business team
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:34.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so, Yasuda Danchou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:39.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How will his first throw turn out? It is rolling but..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:42.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is making a large right turn
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:44.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected of Danchou's bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.88,0:21:47.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It makes a right turn and ends there
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: 14m 60 cm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.54,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Isn't this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.51,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be overshadowed by Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:22:00.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Up next, is Former girls track cycling team Shimano Riimin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:05.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected of a former
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,8 times Champion of women track cycling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:10.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She places her weight on the left side and throws the bicycle out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:12.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Its heading straight forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:16.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But as feared, it veers towards the right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:18.68,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,As expected, it does turn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: 22m 50cm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:22.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She managed to break Danchou's record
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:25.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A rare expression of self-pride
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.25,0:22:25.91,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing, it really took off
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Following that is our 3rd contestant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:30.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ozeki Shingo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.51,0:22:33.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nihon Creed Gymnastics Team
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Director and athlete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:37.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's got good speed and posture
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:39.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He jumps off the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:39.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He jumps off the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:41.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His landing was decisive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:43.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It appeared to be straight for a while but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:42.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Impressive..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:44.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It went quite straight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:44.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It is still continuing on its path but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:48.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end, it has veered towards the right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His was the best out of the contestants
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: 31m
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:54.94,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow, Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:22:57.65,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,As expected
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:58.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The trick is in cleanly letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:00.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By cleanly letting go of the bike from the back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:02.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He managed to clinch the best record of 31 m
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:06.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,topping the previous record holder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.31,0:23:11.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Lastly, our fourth contestant is BMX pro rider: Ikeda Takahiro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, everyone else is quite serious about this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I am a little nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:37.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In 2016 iBMXff BMX Flatland World Championships 2016, he finished 2nd place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:39.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has also appeared in the Cirque du Soleil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:42.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and possesses the 4 Guinness BMX records
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:44.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He lifts his left leg and attempts his 1st throw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:46.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If only he had thrown it more properly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:48.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Throws
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.54,0:23:50.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ohh, what a blunder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:53.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He is holding his head
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:55.94,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So this type of things happen as well
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really unexpected
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:23:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was damn embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance : 8m 10cm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work just throwing your bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:13.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the 1st try, the highest record is Ozeki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.11,0:24:15.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ikeda Takahiro, the one favored to win is in last
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.11,0:24:17.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What an upsetting turn of events
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:20.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so begins the fateful 2nd round
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.71,0:24:22.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There goes Danchou's 2nd throw
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.68,0:24:24.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Its still going
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:25.45,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing, its still going
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:27.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Its looking good
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.62,0:24:28.74,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Still Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.31,0:24:30.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It makes a large turn but he managed to get good distance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.94,0:24:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,RIGHT ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.60,0:24:36.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His record is 34m 30cm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.11,0:24:40.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taking over Ozeki , he is now the top record holder
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:44.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Following that, is Track cyclist Shimano's 2nd try
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.28,0:24:46.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,She wasn't able to improve her record
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.00,0:24:49.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The result is 18m 40cm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.22,0:24:50.05,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It definitely turns towards the right
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.05,0:24:52.05,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Everyone does seem to end at the right
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.94,0:24:52.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You can see everyone's record up to now
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.14,0:24:56.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The remaining two are Ozeki the gymnast and Ikeda the BMX Pro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.85,0:24:58.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Who will prevail in the end!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.57,0:25:02.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Dark horse Gymnast Ozeki begins his 2nd try
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.31,0:25:03.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he come out on top?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.77,0:25:06.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The crux lies in maintaining speed when you let go
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.62,0:25:08.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here he goes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.22,0:25:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How will it turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.62,0:25:12.62,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Good,He did well
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.42,0:25:13.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Its so good that it looks like a ghost is really riding the bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.85,0:25:15.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Well done achieving such a distance
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.57,0:25:16.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It isn't turning still
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.80,0:25:20.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ahh~ It hit the wall on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.40,0:25:19.80,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Splendid
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.97,0:25:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance : 51m 80cm
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.80,0:25:30.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Once again, Ozeki achieves the top with an immeasurable big throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.68,0:25:34.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The last contestant BMX Ikeda takes the spotlight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.68,0:25:37.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With his pride which brought him to the World's BMX Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.55,0:25:40.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Even with his 1st throw,it looked like it was going to go well
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.42,0:25:39.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His 1st throw surprisingly turned out to be a failure
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.57,0:25:42.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want to feel like a failure again
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.45,0:25:44.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When he's cornered
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.14,0:25:46.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here goes Ikeda's 2nd try : how would it turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.20,0:25:47.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's going straight forward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:49.94,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow that's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.11,0:25:49.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,BMX
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.08,0:25:50.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ikeda's 2nd try
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.31,0:25:52.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How would it turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.31,0:25:54.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's properly rolling straight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.31,0:25:55.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This is truly
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.94,0:25:57.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,ghost cycling
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.82,0:26:02.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It slid and crashed into the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.22,0:26:05.22,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is truly the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.25,0:26:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance : 50m 40cm
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.22,0:26:08.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.17,0:26:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we just call that a home run?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.82,0:26:16.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this case where two contestants have hit the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.37,0:26:19.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We shall now conduct an extended round
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.08,0:26:23.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Luckily for us, the rain has cleared and we have shifted to an empty parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.37,0:26:28.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Gymnast Ozaki VS BMX Ikeda in the 1st round tiebreaker
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.62,0:26:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the distance looking from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.25,0:26:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.48,0:26:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We can throw however far we want to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.31,0:26:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The ground is bumpy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.82,0:26:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to "read" the line the bike is gonna follow
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.94,0:26:42.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Into the extended round
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.02,0:26:45.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By lot drawing again, Ozaki is to be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.48,0:26:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, going for it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.08,0:26:50.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Ghostriding Tournament's first throw in the outer field
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.22,0:26:52.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In front of him, there are no longer any walls to stop him
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.48,0:26:54.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end, what kind of record will he be able to show us
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.85,0:26:56.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ozaki's challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.34,0:26:58.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has successfully fallen from the back and thrown out his bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.57,0:26:59.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ozaki's challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.40,0:27:01.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He has successfully fallen from the back and thrown out his bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.40,0:27:03.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The ghost bicycle is moving but
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.40,0:27:06.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,it has ended up making a really large right turn
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.80,0:27:11.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and it has stopped, the ghost has stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.80,0:27:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance :  37m 70cm
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.71,0:27:19.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ozaki was unable to extend his past record
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.00,0:27:25.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Following that act is BMX Ikeda
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.77,0:27:30.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If he manages to break Ozaki's record, his win would be set in stone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.45,0:27:31.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Who will be our 1st ghostriding champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.94,0:27:33.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ozaki or Ikeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.11,0:27:37.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He's lifting his left leg and has let go
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.22,0:27:39.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He made a winning pose
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.02,0:27:41.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He lifted his left leg and has let go
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.02,0:27:41.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Its heading straight forward
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.97,0:27:43.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He made a winning pose
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.42,0:27:45.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Its smoothly pulling ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.20,0:27:47.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's truly a ghost riding the bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.48,0:27:49.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's still making distance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.48,0:27:51.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And finally it has fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.54,0:27:54.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How is his record?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.45,0:28:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: 53m 30cm
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.80,0:28:05.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And with that, the crowned champion for the 1st ever Ghostriding Tournament is:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.71,0:28:09.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,BMX Pro Rider: Ikeda Takahiro
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.08,0:28:10.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In conclusion:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.65,0:28:14.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ghostriding competitions are somewhat exciting but
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.65,0:28:18.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,good kids should not follow in their example
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.88,0:28:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.71,0:28:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes yes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.68,0:28:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.51,0:28:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.88,0:28:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was underwhelmingly soft
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.38,0:28:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably softspoken
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.38,0:28:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.51,0:28:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were talking to me, you stared intensely
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.51,0:28:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, when I replied, it became a half-hearted response
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.57,0:28:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, the gymnast
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.00,0:28:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,performed better than anticipated
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.94,0:28:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What he did: Jumping off the back of the bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.42,0:28:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the bicycle flip upwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.77,0:28:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.00,0:28:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When he let go, it went smoothly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.85,0:28:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your job properly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.77,0:28:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think its due to the fact that he jumped off from the back
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.28,0:28:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there a moment where he needed to flip upwards from the handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.25,0:28:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.60,0:28:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't flip it and just let go like this
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.60,0:29:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.45,0:29:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tragic
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.08,0:29:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This situation is wretched
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.51,0:29:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Joker, he let go like this
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.65,0:29:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore it could go straight upon release
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.68,0:29:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening to you, ghost comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.62,0:29:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one hell of a nickname
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.14,0:29:18.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Moving on, proving and disproving common theories from our audience
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.48,0:29:21.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The viewer's theory corner
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.08,0:29:23.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tonight's presenter is:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.74,0:29:28.34,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Tamura Kenji
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.34,0:29:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.28,0:29:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, this is kind of sudden but
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.77,0:29:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you are celebrities in the show business
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.71,0:29:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been requested to have a portrait of you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.11,0:29:42.91,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.11,0:29:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Downtown-san right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.91,0:29:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Degawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.05,0:29:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have appeared a lot on magazines
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.02,0:29:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,which are mostly made from user submissions
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.85,0:29:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I see
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.85,0:29:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of types of portraits
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.85,0:29:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those who specialize in exaggerating
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.05,0:29:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.40,0:30:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's a exaggerated caricature of Hamada-san
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.42,0:30:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is how it turned out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.75,0:30:00.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.62,0:30:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing by the way
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.55,0:30:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it's him instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.25,0:30:11.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't the caricature weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.02,0:30:14.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you mean weak! I don't have fat lips like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.09,0:30:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I wonder how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.42,0:30:16.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is it really exaggerated?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.66,0:30:21.70,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why did my lips become like that? Look look! They're normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.33,0:30:21.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.73,0:30:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.93,0:30:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyes look like they've been pushed to the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.02,0:30:31.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah the eyes right? The parts on my face are gathered in the center so it's becomes that way
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.68,0:30:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.51,0:30:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're asked who this is, you definitely answer Hamada-san
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.48,0:30:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.36,0:30:36.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.96,0:30:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This time right, I have brought with me a theory about this type of drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.48,0:30:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.29,0:30:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Theory : A caricaturist's exaggeration will lessen if the client being drawn is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.67,0:30:51.41,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.42,0:30:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Being careful like "Will it be okay? His nose is kinda big but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.05,0:30:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't they be careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.39,0:31:01.78,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah that's a tough situation as a professional isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.67,0:31:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.78,0:31:04.78,Hamada,,0,0,0,,A person who looks kinda scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.78,0:31:06.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's because angry people will get angry
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.48,0:31:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you kill a person instantly but...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.61,0:31:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...if you just...break their precious right arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.88,0:31:15.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You mumbled your words so I didn't get what the hell you're trying to say
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.30,0:31:15.22,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You can't mumble
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.93,0:31:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah you're scary...You comedy-yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.49,0:31:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if its a little,won't you let up
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.29,0:31:27.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We're testing the theory that a caricaturist's exaggeration will lessen if the client being drawn is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.30,0:31:33.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time, with the help of an owner of a portrait shop
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.52,0:31:35.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We will investigate with hidden cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.11,0:31:38.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our first target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.44,0:31:41.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...a portrait artist...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.40,0:31:39.43,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Waah, it looks like him
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.43,0:31:41.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Isn't the exaggeration too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.30,0:31:47.91,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,But this guy is kind of scary right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.38,0:31:43.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...who has drawn these portraits
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.37,0:31:48.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And our helper will be this man with a scary look
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.79,0:31:53.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His hair can be called a "bar code head"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.63,0:31:54.73,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I mean yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.23,0:32:00.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now we get our guy inside with an over the top yakuza feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.04,0:32:00.82,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Over the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.48,0:32:05.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to draw an usual caricature with a scary man as his subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.68,0:32:07.21,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Will he? I want him to...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.00,0:32:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey don't fucking sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.46,0:32:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of touch would you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.10,0:32:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just draw me as I am
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.16,0:32:22.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now that we've shown the strong look, the portrait drawing starts
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.60,0:32:25.25,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But it'd be weird if he drew thick hairs
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.25,0:32:27.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And it's done
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.02,0:32:30.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What kind of portrait has it turned out to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.59,0:32:30.12,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's probably stressed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.05,0:32:17.59,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,With a bar code head?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.61,0:32:22.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You really can't draw here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.75,0:32:35.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There is a little bit of exaggeration but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.42,0:32:38.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...the hair should've been drawn even less however...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.99,0:32:39.89,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's definitely like that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.74,0:32:42.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...in this portrait it has reversely gotten thicker
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.68,0:32:43.74,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He put more hair on it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.14,0:32:46.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There is zero exaggeration of the bar code-head
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.09,0:32:48.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.03,0:32:51.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,has the exaggeration gotten weaker? When we ask him...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.29,0:32:50.83,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's a bit hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.18,0:32:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the drawing process?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.89,0:32:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard to draw him
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.12,0:32:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.98,0:32:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was a scary man
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.30,0:32:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.01,0:32:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it was
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.43,0:33:01.44,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So it WAS hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.43,0:33:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was to test if when a scary person comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.48,0:33:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.65,0:33:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...will you hold back a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.33,0:33:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You definitely hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.09,0:33:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The hardest ones to draw are the scary people
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.10,0:33:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.30,0:33:17.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that, here is the result when we make him draw holding nothing back
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.73,0:33:17.81,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I wonder how different it'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.62,0:33:20.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He of course draws the receding hairline...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.29,0:33:23.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...but also a very round face and pronounced eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.60,0:33:29.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We can easily see that he was really holding back before
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.84,0:33:28.33,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He almost looks like a foreigner
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.00,0:33:33.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How about this scary man?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.55,0:33:35.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The features that stand out are...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.92,0:33:38.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...the big nose and his underbite
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.05,0:33:40.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,His chin sticks out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.25,0:33:41.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And our next artist is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.94,0:33:43.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...this man
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.04,0:33:47.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He already has drawn people with protruding chins...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.89,0:33:51.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...to an extreme, but what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.26,0:33:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about a person's characteristics so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.17,0:34:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...it becomes a minus for the exaggeration
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.03,0:34:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The exaggeration?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.03,0:34:00.02,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's saying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.57,0:34:00.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's pushing forward
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.16,0:34:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can display it as a good point of that person
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.87,0:34:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is a person of his own so...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.85,0:34:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you ask which it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.68,0:34:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...we think of it as a plus
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.55,0:34:15.63,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's really freaking out
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.12,0:34:17.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Quibbling along trying to insure his safety
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.76,0:34:23.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end, how did the caricature turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.70,0:34:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of drawing has it turned out to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.32,0:34:28.81,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.58,0:34:30.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though there was alot of material...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.30,0:34:32.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...it seems that he was holding back
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.48,0:34:33.93,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for Shohara-san
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.45,0:34:36.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Asking him after we explain the prank...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.73,0:34:36.84,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,You can't do that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.72,0:34:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from a program called "Wednesday Downtown"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.18,0:34:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.84,0:34:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there anything odd that happened to you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.56,0:34:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the customers uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.62,0:34:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed to be in a special line of work
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.36,0:34:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I kinda thought of him like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.40,0:34:55.73,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What was all that guaranteeing safety
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.36,0:34:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were for real, would you exaggerated a little bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.45,0:35:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly I would yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.93,0:35:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He has quite a unique face
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.71,0:35:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There are alot of high-potential parts but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.07,0:35:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...they don't really stand out with what I've drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.71,0:35:13.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With that, when we have him draw no holds barred...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.01,0:35:16.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...here is the result!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.01,0:35:15.15,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I wonder how it'll turn out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.97,0:35:21.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Certainly when you compare them, the size of the nose, the look of his eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.29,0:35:19.06,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Aahh...His nose and...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.31,0:35:25.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and also the size of his chin makes it easy to see that he was holding back
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.22,0:35:22.94,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The teeth are showing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.94,0:35:25.33,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The size is completely different
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.33,0:35:27.63,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.41,0:35:29.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When we continue with our investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.91,0:35:32.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We can't really find any caricaturists...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.53,0:35:35.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...that actually do their job when faced with a scary looking man
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.96,0:35:41.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Lastly, we will use this man for our experiment
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.43,0:35:42.98,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He isn't scary at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.51,0:35:45.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The comedian (Einstein's Inada)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.08,0:35:48.41,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's put on there isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.93,0:35:48.41,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why is there a...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.08,0:35:49.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This ugly ass comedian from Kansai...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.19,0:35:53.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...will be taking on the role of a yakuza underling
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.46,0:35:57.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With an already extremely protruding chin...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.14,0:35:51.51,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,If you made it that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.98,0:35:54.05,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.17,0:35:55.66,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's really made him scary
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.92,0:36:01.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...and a head with signs of a weird kind of balding.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.60,0:36:06.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But also with a giant fake mole
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.86,0:36:01.60,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.92,0:36:09.68,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,If they really made it like this what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.25,0:36:13.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What will happen when a person with a face completely full of exaggerated parts shows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.45,0:36:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.35,0:36:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it fast I ain't got time
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.13,0:36:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.61,0:36:18.90,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're not letting him talk
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.13,0:36:24.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We pushed his scary character
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.08,0:36:28.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What has that face been made into?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.95,0:36:25.85,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Scary! That kind of mole is definitely scaring him
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.45,0:36:29.01,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The fact that it's on the side is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.66,0:36:36.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Somehow his unique chin has been clearly drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.21,0:36:40.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that the fear factor was not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.82,0:36:41.14,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's..scared..right
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.49,0:36:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a bit scary yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.92,0:36:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.52,0:36:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he was a scary person...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.98,0:36:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you go all out...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.38,0:36:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...alot of things can go wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.51,0:36:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some points where I held back
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.58,0:36:52.61,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He was holding back
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.53,0:36:52.61,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's not gone full force
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.81,0:36:57.87,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,How will it become?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.18,0:36:55.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This was actually held back
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.91,0:37:02.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Actually when told, the balding, the nose and the chin are clearly visible but
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.13,0:37:04.86,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It doesn't actually look that much different from the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.33,0:37:06.96,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.86,0:37:06.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The real man was too amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.64,0:37:11.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So there was an illusion of exaggeration
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.77,0:37:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were a person who laughed a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.40,0:37:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...I could've probably gone all out
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.96,0:37:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I think to myself "This man is OK" I can go at it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.56,0:37:22.80,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He can tell that...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.18,0:37:24.62,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.85,0:37:26.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here's the version we made him do afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.81,0:37:29.68,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's sticking out goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.38,0:37:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not fitting in
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.58,0:37:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You really held back didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.01,0:37:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you had to be careful because of me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.79,0:37:33.48,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,His hair is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.73,0:37:43.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That means, even professional caricaturists
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.54,0:37:46.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will hold back with their exaggeration
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.42,0:37:51.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And also the exaggerated version looks more real
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.92,0:37:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.96,0:37:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The quality seems to disappear a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.80,0:38:01.07,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ebisu-san, can you draw portraits?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.07,0:38:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens from time to time actually
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.30,0:38:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The hardest parts are when a female customer comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.88,0:38:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...even when a weird woman comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.82,0:38:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...I try to draw them pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.37,0:38:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you actually want to draw them ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.72,0:38:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...actually...yeah I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.61,0:38:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an honest guy isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.19,0:38:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do any of you own any point cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.20,0:38:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I do own some
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.15,0:38:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The bakery near me has one...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.91,0:38:43.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.83,0:38:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't do it do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.62,0:38:46.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't she looking to up her popularity with that kind of move?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.60,0:38:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop doing stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.94,0:38:53.17,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Then, do you know how much you pay for a cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.87,0:38:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.17,0:38:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.12,0:38:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know a cabbage's price
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.18,0:39:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you're not looking at how much it is when you're buying it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.09,0:39:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I DO look
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.11,0:39:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I do look at the price but since I want cabbages I buy it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.31,0:39:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be 1000 yen for one cabbage would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.78,0:39:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really staring me down
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.40,0:39:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were smiling when talking to Matsumoto-san
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.17,0:39:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She got excited and really stared me down
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.67,0:39:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I have brought a theory about those point cards
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.10,0:39:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is:
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.41,0:39:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Theory: There are plenty of point cards that set goals that are impossible to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.22,0:39:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ones that make you think "Can you really save up from that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.30,0:39:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"How many times will I have to go there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.93,0:39:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There are plenty like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.68,0:39:41.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We will investigate some point cards that are hard to accomplish or are plain weird after this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.70,0:39:35.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh really...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.32,0:39:48.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We will investigate the theory that there are plenty of point cards that set goals that are impossible to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.41,0:39:53.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, when we search for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.05,0:39:57.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...we found a car parts shop that gives you 10000 yen discount if you spend 2 million yen at their shop
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.58,0:40:05.17,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's pretty strict isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.58,0:40:05.17,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh it's that kind of package
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.48,0:40:01.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Spending 500,000 yen will get you a 5000 yen gift certificate
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.78,0:40:04.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,at this store specializing in bags
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.06,0:40:08.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Of course, we found numerous ridiculous point cards here...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.80,0:40:14.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...but within that, this is the one that beats the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.73,0:40:17.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In Osaka, there's a maid cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.19,0:40:19.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,called "Nadia"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.86,0:40:25.92,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,There's a option for 500 points
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:24.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have a system where if you spend 500 yen, you earn one point
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.24,0:40:28.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have various prizes from 5 points to those with special privileges starting at 200 points
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.35,0:40:30.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Basically, if you exchange 100,000 yen worth of points
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.88,0:40:32.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You get a photoshoot with the maids
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.13,0:40:36.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, 150,000 yen will get you a lunch date with a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.68,0:40:41.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,250,000 yen and you can hang out with a maid for an entire day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.21,0:40:47.40,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's pretty cool
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.63,0:40:44.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the prices continue to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.98,0:40:47.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are still goals which require more points
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.59,0:40:53.07,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Vacation to a foreign country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.83,0:40:51.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Taking a maid on a vacation in a foreign country will require 3000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.09,0:40:56.87,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.89,0:40:56.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy77\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\pos(940.5,988)}(14.000 USD or 10.000 Pounds)
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.89,0:40:56.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In actuality, you need 1,500,000 yen in points.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.90,0:41:01.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, you will not be able to go alone with a maid,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.72,0:41:06.72,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He comes along??
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.61,0:41:04.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The store owner will tag along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.07,0:41:07.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In addition, all travel expenses
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.00,0:41:10.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and accommodation charges will be covered by the customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.95,0:41:12.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Who would wanna do this??
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.72,0:41:18.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even though these rules being so strict, is there anyone who would take this trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.87,0:41:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone ever saved up for the trip to a foreign country?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.54,0:41:21.75,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.75,0:41:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there have been a few
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.67,0:41:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tagged along to places like Hong Kong, Hawaii, and Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.81,0:41:36.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There have been 10 people so far that have earned this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.47,0:41:40.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By the way, of the customers currently in the maid cafe today
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.85,0:41:43.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How many points have they saved so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.40,0:41:46.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We asked them to let us see their cards
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.06,0:41:47.20,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Noooo....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.35,0:41:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,308 points
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.52,0:41:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.97,0:41:53.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With a cost of 150,000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.73,0:41:56.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he's saved up over 300 points
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.49,0:42:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you get now that you've saved 300 points?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.74,0:42:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go on a lunch date
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.91,0:42:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,together with a maid to a store I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.74,0:42:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Are you gonna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.47,0:42:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about it before, but now I'm reconsidering
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.37,0:42:14.30,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.35,0:42:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can go to several places if I use 500 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.40,0:42:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so these 300 points
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.52,0:42:23.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.89,0:42:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use them once, they'll decrease
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.81,0:42:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How much have you spent so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.06,0:42:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy77\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\pos(736.5,908)}(9 350 USD or 6 650 Pounds)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.06,0:42:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to 1 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.22,0:42:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel satisfied with your purchases?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.33,0:42:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Very much so
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.44,0:42:32.76,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.81,0:42:35.69,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They are used to the high price point
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.71,0:42:33.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The cost is high...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.68,0:42:37.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but the customers seems satisfied with paying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.04,0:42:42.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, as we continue our investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.63,0:42:47.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We have discovered a number of genre specific point cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.07,0:42:49.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,To begin with
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.21,0:42:58.67,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Their sensei sure is convincing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.13,0:42:57.12,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.49,0:42:54.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,at a West African traditional drumming practice course for "Djembe"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.94,0:42:57.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,1000 yen is equal to 1 point
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.12,0:42:59.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you save 100,000 yen worth of points...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.95,0:43:03.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You receive a big Djembe drum
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.10,0:43:05.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, the course is only once a week
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.88,0:43:10.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and one lesson is 2000 yen, so it will take 50 weeks to save the points.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.34,0:43:15.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Which means if you go to every class without skipping a week, it will take 350 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.97,0:43:19.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In addition, the expiration date on the offer is in 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.21,0:43:20.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,A limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.37,0:43:22.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With this ridiculous setting...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.37,0:43:28.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...no one has been able to obtain the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.34,0:43:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have the points...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.95,0:43:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,by May of next year right? If you keep saving?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.36,0:43:36.67,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.36,0:43:36.67,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.08,0:43:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if I keep at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.96,0:43:40.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Moving on, our next point card comes from this cemetery
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.14,0:43:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Our point card is called "Mairi Point Card". If you go around the cemetery once...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.44,0:43:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You get 30 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.56,0:43:54.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy77\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\pos(978,994)}(To pray)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.56,0:43:54.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Mairi Point". Combining the names "Mairi" and "Mile"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.12,0:44:00.70,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Don't bully them
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.26,0:43:58.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy77\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\pos(721.5,992)}(Pray mile points)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.26,0:43:58.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It comes together to form a hilarious name.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.69,0:44:00.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you go around the gravesite 40 times...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.76,0:44:04.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You can receive flowers worth 1200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.65,0:44:10.89,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.89,0:44:13.72,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.89,0:44:08.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A point card that will truly make your ancestors happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.72,0:44:16.12,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.23,0:44:14.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Others: A candy store which will give a 50 yen off coupon if you come 20 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.52,0:44:17.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A cycle track and bike store which
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.97,0:44:20.10,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.80,0:44:20.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will give you a "beckoning cat" if you come 240 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.27,0:44:22.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, a snake cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.62,0:44:25.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,which will let you touch the snakes as much as you want if you come 20 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.98,0:44:29.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are many special point cards indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.48,0:44:33.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And there is one within those that is even more special
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.72,0:44:37.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or rather, more like an insane point card
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.66,0:44:58.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An everyday goods shop in Saitama prefecture, Cosucoji
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.61,0:44:58.21,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,C-cosu?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.21,0:45:01.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In this store, 1000 yen equals 1 point.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.48,0:45:04.08,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's going to be quite difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.26,0:45:04.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And 60,000 yen will allow you to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.23,0:45:10.18,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They've got a decent amount
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.02,0:45:07.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,exchange your points for various interesting choices
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.66,0:45:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a beard right now right...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.48,0:45:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an option where you can shave my beard
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.57,0:45:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really... is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.07,0:45:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.34,0:45:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been a few people who have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.80,0:45:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.21,0:45:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.66,0:45:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibaragi Dialect Lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.99,0:45:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have people saved up for this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.96,0:45:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.34,0:45:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718.5,694)}No one has exchanged for this option, but you keep it on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.43,0:45:33.94,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.45,0:45:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.26,0:45:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm leaving it on there just in case someone does want it, I think it'll be interesting, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.55,0:45:38.12,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A store owner who naturally laughs at his own jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.12,0:45:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a dad
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.90,0:45:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the prizes is a life consulting session with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.29,0:45:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really an amazing person. Very meticulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.00,0:45:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How many points is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.28,0:45:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.60,0:45:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,120 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.24,0:45:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,120..
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.64,0:45:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at it from the other side, would you take this prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.26,0:45:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.13,0:46:03.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, there is the option to do "Ghost Calisthenics" with the owner's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.21,0:46:08.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Or force the owner to cross dress for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.32,0:46:11.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are many options that make the owner incredibly nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.61,0:46:13.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And lastly
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.17,0:46:16.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An overnight tour of the Asahiyama Zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.59,0:46:19.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fscx60\fscy77\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\4a&HFF&\pos(718.5,990)}(84.000 USD or 60.000 Pounds)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.59,0:46:19.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It costs 9 million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.08,0:46:27.11,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.75,0:46:24.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An inconceivable amount, this is a hellish privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.86,0:46:26.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There you have it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.22,0:46:29.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of ridiculous point cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.55,0:46:33.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,as well as point cards that fall short of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.76,0:46:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty interesting don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.79,0:46:38.66,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.66,0:46:42.58,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is it ok for the maid cafe to be doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.58,0:46:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.73,0:46:47.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Legally speaking is that even allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.65,0:46:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean them taking a trip with the customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.86,0:46:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it feel like human trafficking?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.05,0:46:54.65,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Human trafficking..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.52,0:46:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.22,0:46:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too much huh..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.65,0:46:57.93,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.36,0:47:00.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next week, an "Audience Theory" special!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.95,0:47:04.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Given a single bean every 10 seconds, you can continue eating forever".
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.64,0:47:06.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Being the winner of a race show...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.85,0:47:09.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,people you don't know will contact you."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.28,0:47:14.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"If you drag someone around with a blindfold, they won't notice that they've returned home"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.36,0:47:17.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, "It's better to wash a Panda "
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.24,0:47:19.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Pa-ko is the weakest stare-down player",
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.52,0:47:23.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Small Saving" Theory, and more to investigate next week.
